     console.log('Tags:', this.tags);
   }
   ```

4. **Verify EventEmitter**: Ensure `setListTag` is correctly set up and used. If you intend to handle the click event, make sure the parent component is listening for this event.

### Summary

The template itself looks correct, assuming `tags` is an array of strings. If you still encounter issues, focus on verifying the data source and component logic to ensure the `tags` property is correctly populated and passed to the template. If there are specific issues or errors, feel free to provide more details for further assistance.

